1884.query: SELECT COUNT(t1.user_id) FROM ratings as t1 inner JOIN movies as t2 ON t1.movie_id = t2.movie_id WHERE t2.movie_title = 'A Way of Life' AND t1.user_trialist = 1

1885.query: SELECT name FROM users WHERE age > 25
